and everything you do

00:00:12.241 --> 00:00:13.877 position:24% line:89% align:start
is really precise.

00:00:13.877 --> 00:00:16.779 position:10% line:83% align:start
You're probably well-suited
to this kind of job.

00:00:16.779 --> 00:00:20.016 position:19% line:83% align:start
Wait, are you actually
giving me a compliment...?

00:00:20.016 --> 00:00:22.419 position:24% line:83% align:start
Try not to let it
go to your head.

00:00:22.419 --> 00:00:24.856 position:5% line:83% align:start
