so it's only natural

00:00:24.856 --> 00:00:26.191 position:21% line:89% align:start
that you get better.

00:00:26.191 --> 00:00:27.425 position:33% line:89% align:start
Fair enough.

00:00:32.733 --> 00:00:35.102 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Tomoya]: All the guys who
sat next to me in school

00:00:35.102 --> 00:00:37.005 position:7% line:89% align:start
