00:00:37.005 --> 00:00:40.308 position:19% line:83% align:start
They're probably going
to college in other towns.

00:00:40.308 --> 00:00:43.412 position:19% line:83% align:start
But... even if I'm the
only one who stayed here...

00:00:43.412 --> 00:00:46.148 position:10% line:89% align:start
that doesn't mean I'm alone.

00:00:46.148 --> 00:00:48.217 position:19% line:83% align:start
There are other people
working and sweating

00:00:48.217 --> 00:00:50.520 position:21% line:83% align:start
and getting covered
in grime just like me.

00:00:50.520 --> 00:00:54.625 position:7% line:83% align:start
