at the beach!

00:02:44.160 --> 00:02:46.595 position:19% line:83% align:start
They sound so similar,
I don't know which to pick!

00:02:46.595 --> 00:02:47.930 position:30% line:83% align:start
@But that last
oneúdoesn't fit at all.

00:02:47.930 --> 00:02:49.800 position:16% line:83% align:start
