with Barbara Fujioka?!

00:02:52.436 --> 00:02:54.072 position:10% line:89% align:start
@Is that evenúa real person?

00:02:54.072 --> 00:02:55.907 position:10% line:83% align:start
You can have Barbara, I just
want to play with Nagisa!

00:02:55.907 --> 00:02:58.509 position:10% line:83% align:start
I've been so lonely without
her; I'll do anything!

00:02:58.509 --> 00:03:00.612 position:24% line:89% align:start
I-I'm sorry, Dad!

00:03:00.612 --> 00:03:03.983 position:5% line:83% align:start
Don't mind him, he's just having
a tough time letting Nagisa go

00:03:03.983 --> 00:03:05.585 position:19% line:89% align:start
after all these years.

00:03:05.585 --> 00:03:07.821 position:13% line:83% align:start
It's only natural for you
to spend time together.

00:03:07.821 --> 00:03:09.056 position:38% line:89% align:start
I see...

00:03:09.056 --> 00:03:11.659 position:7% line:89% align:start
So I guess I gotta share, huh?

00:03:17.365 --> 00:03:20.570 position:13% line:77% align:start
[Tomoya]: Good to see you
parents are as energetic as
ever.

00:03:21.905 --> 00:03:24.408 position:30% line:83% align:start
What's wrong?
Something on your mind?

00:03:26.643 --> 00:03:30.448 position:7% line:89% align:start
I uh... think we need to talk.

00:03:30.448 --> 00:03:32.718 position:21% line:83% align:start
What is it? You need
a swimsuit for the beach?

00:03:32.718 --> 00:03:35.321 position:13% line:89% align:start
Mm-mmm. No, it's not that.

00:03:35.321 --> 00:03:38.091 position:19% line:83% align:start
Ah, I mean... now that
you mention it,

00:03:38.091 --> 00:03:39.493 position:16% line:89% align:start
I could use a new one...

00:03:39.493 --> 00:03:41.328 position:21% line:83% align:start
All right. I get off
work early tomorrow,

00:03:41.328 --> 00:03:42.262 position:24% line:83% align:start
