your school swimsuit, right?

00:03:47.536 --> 00:03:51.608 position:16% line:83% align:start
[Nagisa]: Yeah. But it's
not bad. I don't mind.

00:03:51.608 --> 00:03:54.211 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Tomoya]: I mind. I want my
girlfriend to look cute.

00:03:54.211 --> 00:03:56.647 position:16% line:83% align:start
