00:04:09.163 --> 00:04:11.398 position:24% line:89% align:start
No, that's not it.

00:04:11.398 --> 00:04:13.968 position:21% line:83% align:start
Not about swimsuits
after all? Oh, then...

00:04:13.968 --> 00:04:15.570 position:35% line:89% align:start
Tomoya...

00:04:19.308 --> 00:04:21.011 position:13% line:89% align:start
I brought this up before,

00:04:21.011 --> 00:04:22.946 position:19% line:83% align:start
but have you seen your
father since you moved

00:04:22.946 --> 00:04:24.581 position:19% line:89% align:start
to your new apartment?

00:04:24.581 --> 00:04:26.117 position:27% line:83% align:start
Well, did you at
least give him a call

00:04:26.117 --> 00:04:28.352 position:19% line:83% align:start
to let him know where
you're living now?

00:04:29.153 --> 00:04:30.989 position:35% line:89% align:start
Not yet...

00:04:30.989 --> 00:04:33.659 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Tomoya]: You understand the
situation, don't you?

00:04:33.659 --> 00:04:36.361 position:10% line:83% align:start
We're pretty much completely
estranged from each other.

00:04:36.361 --> 00:04:38.498 position:24% line:83% align:start
It's not something
that's gonna change.

00:04:39.033 --> 00:04:40.167 position:35% line:89% align:start
But, you-

00:04:40.167 --> 00:04:42.069 position:10% line:89% align:start
