a job offer that good again.

00:23:56.709 --> 00:23:57.875 position:30% line:89% align:start
It's not fair.

00:23:57.875 --> 00:23:59.812 position:24% line:83% align:start
Well, if your life
can change once,

00:23:59.812 --> 00:24:02.048 position:24% line:83% align:start
then it can change
again for the better.

00:24:02.048 --> 00:24:04.818 position:5% line:83% align:start
[Akio]: Look at that, just like
me, when I was that age.

00:24:04.818 --> 00:24:08.155 position:10% line:83% align:start
